1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,940
A smart community decision platform for faster, clearer city operations.

2
00:00:07,940 --> 00:00:19,720
Cities have data, but decisions are slowed by scattered systems and delayed interpretation.

3
00:00:19,720 --> 00:00:29,270
One clean cockpit turns civic signals into explainable, human-approved action.

4
00:00:29,270 --> 00:00:39,760
The dashboard focuses attention on the highest-risk ward instead of overwhelming the viewer.

5
00:00:39,760 --> 00:00:47,970
Ward-level risk scores reveal where response teams should look first.

6
00:00:47,970 --> 00:00:58,700
Actions are ranked by urgency, owner, expected impact, and supporting evidence.

7
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:07,390
The report view creates a shareable civic brief with sources and next steps.

8
00:01:07,390 --> 00:01:18,480
Dashboard, Risk Map, Actions, Reports, and FAQ guide the complete demo flow.

9
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:30,720
30 seeded records across complaints, traffic, waste, utilities, environment, actions, and documents.

10
00:01:30,720 --> 00:01:40,460
The right panel answers questions in plain English with confidence, evidence, and citations.

11
00:01:40,460 --> 00:01:54,210
Cloud Run, BigQuery, Gemini, ADK, Vector Search, Looker, Cloud Storage, IAM, and Logging.

12
00:01:54,210 --> 00:02:05,730
The system recommends and explains, but humans approve civic decisions.

13
00:02:05,730 --> 00:02:13,890
Faster insight, better resource allocation, and clearer community response.

14
00:02:13,890 --> 00:02:24,040
CivicMind AI turns scattered civic data into actionable community intelligence.

